Class Student

java.lang.Object
com.example.cs213_tuition_project_javafx.Student

Direct Known Subclasses:

public abstract class Student extends Object implements Comparable<Student>
Implementation of abstract class Student Contains profile, major , and creditCompleted as parameters Contains abstract methods tuitionDue and isResident Contains methods overrided methods such as toString, equals, compareTo Contains methods to check student standing, if the student is valid, and getter methods

      Returns:
